Package: mail-archiver
Version: 1.0.0-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Madhav Diwan <madhav@decllc.biz>
Depends: python3-flask, gunicorn, isync
Section: mail
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://dec-llc.biz
Description: Self-hosted email archive with full-text search
 Mail Archiver is a self-hosted email archive supporting Gmail, iCloud,
 and Outlook/Hotmail via IMAP. Features SQLite FTS5 search index,
 Microsoft OAuth2, MBOX/EML export, and scheduled sync.
